        <h2>Cars, planes, trucks, and more</h2>
        <p>Browse the same catalog images and product descriptions that powered the original Web Forms sample.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Migration benchmark target</h2>
        <p>This run keeps the generated WingtipToys project shape while repairing the catalog, cart, and account flows in place.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Ready for Playwright</h2>
        <p>The site ships with Bootstrap styling, responsive navigation, and working product imagery for the acceptance suite.</p>
    </div>
</div>
